g.text: Journal Region On-Disk Layout Circular Buffer

ul.li: Checkpointed: Blocks in range [1, j_head) are already flushed to their home locations.
Dirty: Blocks in range [j_head, j_tail) must be replayed on mount if j_sequence is inconsistent.
Block Padding: Every record is aligned to 4096B disk block boundaries.

g.text: Green: Free Space for New Transactions
INVARIANT: j_tail must not overtake j_head (Journal Full)
